'''圭亚那华人'''群体主要是由在19世纪被带到{{link-en|英属圭亚那地区|British Guiana}}的华人劳工的后代们构成。

==历史==
在1853年到1879年间，以广东人为主的14000名华人劳工来到了{{link-en|英属加勒比地区|British West Indies}}（英属西印度），成为了更为大型的契约劳动系统的一部分，为食糖种植园而工作。这些劳工中大多数人的目的地是英属圭亚那地区（圭亚那）和[[特立尼达岛|特立尼达]]。这两个地方前者是在[[拿破仑战争|拿破仑战争]]中从荷兰人手中夺来的，后者是在1797年从西班牙人手中夺来的。<ref>[http://www.everyculture.com/Middle-America-Caribbean/Chinese-in-the-English-Speaking-Caribbean-Orientation.html ''Chinese in the English-Speaking Caribbean - Orientation''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.everyculture.com/Middle-America-Caribbean/Chinese-in-the-English-Speaking-Caribbean-Orientation.html |date=20150226080340 }}<br>[http://www.everyculture.com/Middle-America-Caribbean/Chinese-in-the-English-Speaking-Caribbean-Orientation.html 《说英语的加勒比地区的华人——适应》] {{Wayback|url=http://www.everyculture.com/Middle-America-Caribbean/Chinese-in-the-English-Speaking-Caribbean-Orientation.html |date=20150226080340 }} {{en icon}}</ref>比起其他的英国在加勒比地区的殖民地来，在英属圭亚那地区，他们在种植园待的时间要更长得多，这是因为零售贸易、商品蔬菜经营之类的其他的行业都被葡萄牙人垄断了，因此华人进入不了这些行业。<ref>[http://motherearthtravel.com/guyana/population.htm ''Population of Guyana''] {{Wayback|url=http://motherearthtravel.com/guyana/population.htm |date=20160114153952 }}<br>[http://motherearthtravel.com/guyana/population.htm 《圭亚那的种植园》] {{Wayback|url=http://motherearthtravel.com/guyana/population.htm |date=20160114153952 }} {{en icon}}</ref>由于几乎所有的签约移民的华人都是男子，所以他们有倾向于和东印度人与非洲人进行跨种族结合，因此，圭亚那的华人不像其他群体一样保留了明显的身体特征。<ref>[http://www.everyculture.com/Middle-America-Caribbean/Chinese-in-the-English-Speaking-Caribbean-Settlements.html ''Chinese in the English-Speaking Caribbean - Settlements''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.everyculture.com/Middle-America-Caribbean/Chinese-in-the-English-Speaking-Caribbean-Settlements.html |date=20141202003916 }}<br>[http://www.everyculture.com/Middle-America-Caribbean/Chinese-in-the-English-Speaking-Caribbean-Settlements.html 《说英语的加勒比地区的华人——安身》] {{Wayback|url=http://www.everyculture.com/Middle-America-Caribbean/Chinese-in-the-English-Speaking-Caribbean-Settlements.html |date=20141202003916 }} {{en icon}}</ref>这些华人劳工大多数人最初去的是英属圭亚那地区；不过，在1879年，这样的输入结束了，而华人人口也不断地下降。<ref>[http://countrystudies.us/guyana/31.htm ''Portuguese and Chinese''] {{Wayback|url=http://countrystudies.us/guyana/31.htm |date=20140329223332 }}<br>[http://countrystudies.us/guyana/31.htm 《葡萄牙人与中国人》] {{Wayback|url=http://countrystudies.us/guyana/31.htm |date=20140329223332 }} {{en icon}}</ref>在20世纪60年代，华人占了圭亚那800000个总人口中的0.6个百分点（即约4800人）。

在一份详细介绍荷兰驻[[库尤尼河|库尤尼]]官员的文件中，它提到了圭亚那[[美洲原住民|印第安人]]出售华人奴隶给生活在[[埃塞奎博河|埃塞奎博河]]沿岸的人们，并且这样的业务被允许实行。<ref>{{cite book|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=5JNJAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA127&dq=chinese+slaves+dutch&hl=en&ei=Z2IRTYXpHoKr8AaAluW9Dg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=9&ved=0CE4Q6AEwCA#v=onepage&q=chinese%20slaves%20dutch&f=false|title=''Venezuela-British Guiana Boundary Arbitration: Appendix, pts. 1-2: Documents from Dutch sources. Documents from Spanish sources''|author=Venezuela|year=1898|publisher=The Evening post|page=127|accessdate=2010-07-14|archive-date=2014-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140627161725/http://books.google.com/books?id=5JNJAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA127&dq=chinese+slaves+dutch&hl=en&ei=Z2IRTYXpHoKr8AaAluW9Dg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=9&ved=0CE4Q6AEwCA#v=onepage&q=chinese%20slaves%20dutch&f=false|dead-url=no}}<br>{{cite book|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=5JNJAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA127&dq=chinese+slaves+dutch&hl=en&ei=Z2IRTYXpHoKr8AaAluW9Dg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=9&ved=0CE4Q6AEwCA#v=onepage&q=chinese%20slaves%20dutch&f=false|title=《委内瑞拉-英属圭亚那地区边境仲裁：附件，1-2份：来自荷兰原始资料文件，来自西班牙原始资料文件》|author=委内瑞拉|year=1898年|publisher=晚间邮报|page=127|accessdate=2010年7月14日|archive-date=2014年6月27日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140627161725/http://books.google.com/books?id=5JNJAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA127&dq=chinese+slaves+dutch&hl=en&ei=Z2IRTYXpHoKr8AaAluW9Dg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=9&ved=0CE4Q6AEwCA#v=onepage&q=chinese%20slaves%20dutch&f=false|dead-url=no}} {{en icon}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=ejw8AAAAMAAJ&pg=PA248&dq=chinese+slaves+dutch&hl=en&ei=wWIRTa76B4KC8gbV9MykAw&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=8&ved=0CEkQ6AEwBw#v=onepage&q=chinese%20slaves%20dutch&f=false|title=''Report and accompanying papers of the Commission appointed by the President of the United States "to investigate and report upon the true divisional line between the republic of Venezuela and British Guiana"''|author=United States.